      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW HARKONNEN (7) can keep on winning after an excellent last start success, getting around the 390m at this track in 22.01. Has the ability and looks hard to top. SEATS TWO (2) jumped from a squeeze box but quickly into stride and led until late to place second and beaten a neck (22.30) at this track in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 over 390m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to feature again. PAW IRULAN (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (24.52) in a Grade 5 at Horsham. Should play a prominent role. ON THE RIVER (8) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
